            <lg xml:id="TK304">
<l>nakaiyu muvakaiyuṅ kolluñ ciṉattiṟ</l>
<l>pakaiyu muḷavō piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there a greater enemy than anger, which kills both laughter and joy ?</l>
